  "rationale": "REPAIR: the mission section previously overlaid text on a photograph (no-text-on-photos). It is re-authored as a light-canvas split where the display copy sits on the cream surface with a heavy 'MISSION' ghost-word behind it (text/ghost-on-primary, never on the photo) and a separate flush media panel that carries no text \u2014 resolving the neverDo without changing the rest of the page. Order follows the brief's scroll: an inverse hero bookend (the ONLY inverse section and the ONLY accent carrier) reusing stepped-overlay-statement with its stepped-lines + sanctioned display-title-over-media; about (anchored statement); gallery reusing staggered-caption-columns-3 with the mixed-face {lead/emphasis} masthead and per-column stagger; mission (ghost-word statement, repaired); heritage as a ghost-word era-year timeline (1941\u20132023) via a stat-block run; curator quote-portrait collage; visit info with the Map.jpg panel and a typographic Buy-tickets link; an underline-only newsletter form on a dark panel; and a slash-nav footer. Every non-hero section is primary/panel with no accent, honoring the single-accent and single-inverse fidelity rules; all actions are typographic links (no buttons), no radius/shadow/gradient/hairline devices used."
